name: andb_identity

text.english: \(\texttt{true}\) is the identity element of \(\land\): \[ \forall b \in Bool.\; \texttt{true} \land b = b \]
text.italiano: \(\texttt{true}\) è l'elemento neutro di \(\land\): \[ \forall b \in Bool.\; \texttt{true} \land b = b \]

coq:
Theorem andb_identity : forall b : Bool , true && b = b.
Proof.
reflexivity.
Qed.
